            We assist debtors in lodging formal complaints with the Ministry of Housing and Local Government (KPKT) regarding misconduct, including interest rate violations, financial discrepancies, and legal breaches by Community Credit companies.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
